<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{kiri}}}} when used as a conjunction means that since something happened, nothing has changed.
When used as a particle, @EM{{@HI{{kiri}}}} indicates a strict limitation of a number or quantity.
</p>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{kkiri}}}} is a more colloquial form that can also be more emphatic.
</p>

@BGRNDSTART{{}}

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
Used after a noun or a verb, @EM{{@HI{{kiri}}}} indicates a "cutting off" point or limit and may be translated as "only".

<table class="sentence">
