      @HI{{anoojiisanha,1@KJ{{person}}@EM{{kiri}}de@KJ{{large}}kina@KJ{{house}}ni@KJ{{dwell}}ndeiru.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      That old man lives all by himself in a big house.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</p>

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
@EM{{@HI{{kiri}}}} emphasises a negative meaning and may be translated as "only".
In this usage it may be replaced by <a href="grammar-particle-dake.html">@HI{{dake}}</a>.

<table class="sentence">
